        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "Add Mistral balance metrics",
        "body": "## Summary\n- Add Mistral credit-balance fetching from the authenticated Mistral billing web session.\n- Show Mistral balance in the provider card using the same compact balance treatment as DeepSeek.\n- Preserve existing Mistral menu-bar behavior: Pay-as-you-go shows API spend, while Monthly Plan shows Vibe subscription usage.\n- Preserve the established API-spend fallback when Monthly Plan data is unavailable.\n- Add Mistral visual meter support in the menu-bar icon and provider switcher, so colored bars reflect the selected Mistral metric without treating pay-as-you-go balance as a quota percentage.\n- Update README, provider docs, and Settings copy for API spend, credit balance, and Monthly Plan usage.\n\n## Why\nMistral exposes different billing views for API spend, credit balance, and optional Monthly Plan usage. CodexBar already showed spend/monthly-plan data, but not the available credit balance, which made pay-as-you-go accounts harder to inspect.\n\n## Validation\n- Focused Mistral/UI suite: 114 tests passed.\n- `make check`\n- `plutil -lint Sources/CodexBar/Resources/en.lproj/Localizable.strings`\n- `git diff --check`\n- Ad-hoc signed `./Scripts/package_app.sh`\n- Local patch and full-branch Codex autoreview: clean\n\n## Landing blockers\n- Exact live balance proof needs an authenticated Mistral billing session; the available local browser-cookie path is currently blocked by macOS Keychain authorization.\n- Generic UI/docs/localization files overlap open PRs #1736 and #1803. Rebase after their relevant mainline changes land.\n\n## Screenshot\n### Menu\nBefore\n\n<img width=\"308\" height=\"191\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-06-28 at 15 36 27\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c6302bd7-1181-41aa-b893-571a1b1870eb\" />\n\nAfter\n\n<img width=\"309\" height=\"236\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-06-28 at 14 05 32\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/72693c00-7e03-47b2-bed5-11335d03603f\" />\n\n### Menu-bar icon and provider switcher\nBefore\n\n<img width=\"306\" height=\"118\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-06-28 at 15 36 44\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/8655abfd-7eb7-47a4-a78b-5e22a2c4a1eb\" />\n\nAfter\n\n<img width=\"312\" height=\"119\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-06-28 at 14 45 27\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/8a4a78b7-5728-47d5-11335d03603f\" />\n",
